I am thankful for today 💖 @shop_brij #movetogether #2023goals

The choices we make, define us… I can remember being 19, in WorldWorks (life transformational training) some would say similar to The Landmark Forum. My dyad partner asked me what do you want??? Hungry for change I said “I want peace. I want to be a yoga teacher!”

Naive, excited and not knowing what to expect… I flew to Goa, India at the age of 20 where I completed my first yoga teacher training. My life was forever changed, and since then have had many memorable experiences. 

What was one of the most memorable moments in your life? The choice that led you to this moment?

Hi 🪶✨💖

I am so blessed! These past few days have been magical 🦋 I couldn’t ask for a better group of women to spend the last days of my 20’s… 

Lots of trial and error, but I am grateful for the experiences I have had in my life. Looking back I’ve traveled to many countries, and met some amazing people. Started a business (@shop_brij ) Uprooted and moved to another state during the pandemic and created a new community of new friends. Of course lots laughter and tears shed in between haha… 

I usually get sad around my birthday but this year it sits differently. I can’t wait to look back see what I accomplish! Anyways a big thank you for everyone who has helped me along the way. 

Thank you for all the birthday wishes ✨ #thisis30

D E C E M B E R 1 4

Open Your Heart to Universal Love

We live in a magical, living, vital and personal universe, a world where universal love is real. 

We don’t just live in it, we are a part of it, visibly and tangibly connected to it. The phone call that comes at the right time. A book that teaches us what we need to know. A movie that has a message we need to guide us and open our hearts. An opportunity that arises, at just the right moment. An idea triggered by something someone says or an object we didn’t notice before.

The more we open to Universal, love the more it will be there for us, embracing, loving, holding, guiding us. The more we learn to see it, the more it will be there until we wonder why we never saw it before. 

Open your heart to universal love. 
It’s more than merely there. 
It’s there for you. 
Jump into the arms of a living, magical world, and you leap into the arms of universal love. 
See how real it can be. 

❤️‍🔥
